186
00:11:40,266 --> 00:11:42,768
we weren't having
this supper tonight.

187
00:11:42,769 --> 00:11:44,770
Oh, goodness knows
I usually love it.

188
00:11:44,771 --> 00:11:46,273
But -- but it
interferes, really,

189
00:11:46,274 --> 00:11:48,274
with the trip, if you
know what I mean.

190
00:11:48,775 --> 00:11:50,277
Too many good things at once.

191
00:11:50,278 --> 00:11:52,277
Mm. I felt it, too.

192
00:11:52,278 --> 00:11:53,779
I didn't want
anything to happen.

193
00:11:53,780 --> 00:11:55,282
Just the trip. Nothing else.

194
00:11:55,283 --> 00:11:57,282
Oh, well. We really won't
celebrate tonight.

195
00:11:57,283 --> 00:11:59,785
We'll just eat supper and act
like it was any other evening

196
00:11:59,786 --> 00:12:01,288
and we were home
with the family.

197
00:12:01,289 --> 00:12:04,290
You know what? I'm not
going to sing tonight.

198
00:12:04,791 --> 00:12:06,792
Even if everyone asks
me, I won't sing.

199
00:12:06,793 --> 00:12:09,296
And don't you sing either.
Mnh-mnh.

