212
00:13:28,875 --> 00:13:30,876
♪ Love has got
them floored yet ♪

213
00:13:30,877 --> 00:13:32,878
♪ Sixteen years of
fond attention ♪

214
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:34,880
♪ Is beyond our comprehension ♪

215
00:13:34,881 --> 00:13:38,885
♪ Aren't you bored yet? ♪

216
