00:16:35,061 --> 00:16:37,062
It'd make me sad
if you didn't --

263
00:16:37,063 --> 00:16:38,063
and ashamed.

264
00:16:38,064 --> 00:16:39,566
But it wouldn't matter.

265
00:16:39,567 --> 00:16:41,066
I'd go anyway.

266
00:16:41,067 --> 00:16:44,069
