It's not at all that.

318
00:19:59,765 --> 00:20:02,268
It's my emotions in the chest.

319
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:06,271
Clavdia, you're a throwback.

320
00:20:06,272 --> 00:20:07,774
What's that? What do you mean?

321
00:20:08,274 --> 00:20:10,777
Somebody who doesn't
belong to their own time.

322
00:20:10,778 --> 00:20:14,779
Ours is a new world, Clavdia.
You don't belong in it.

323
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:16,281
Oh, I see.

324
00:20:16,282 --> 00:20:18,283
You mean I'm rather
old-fashioned

325
00:20:18,284 --> 00:20:20,286
and romantic, rather.

326
00:20:21,287 --> 00:20:22,789
Yeah.

327
00:21:28,854 --> 00:21:30,355
No.

328
00:21:30,356 --> 00:21:33,359
I've told you -- you
cannot come along.

329
00:21:34,860 --> 00:21:36,861
I'm always too young.

330
00:21:36,862 --> 00:21:39,364
