334
00:22:17,905 --> 00:22:19,904
I'll bring everybody
a present.

335
00:22:19,905 --> 00:22:21,406
Don't get your feet wet.

336
00:22:21,407 --> 00:22:23,408
And take care of yourselves.

337
00:22:23,409 --> 00:22:26,911
